            <main><article class="main-content"><h1 class="">District News</h1>
        <p class="">Things are constantly moving in our growing district! This is the page where we keep you informed about upcoming events, important school news and awards, and much more; bookmark us, and be sure to check back often!</p>
        <p class="button"><a href="/Human-Resources" title="" alt="Human Resources page" target="_blank">Now Hiring</a></p>
        <div class="pom-container">
<div class="newsItem" id="signaturefieldtrips">
	<div class="newstitle">Signature Field Trips</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class=""><p class="">Attention, future 6th and 7th graders! As a result of the current situation and the uncertainty of how next year will start, we are postponing the signature field trips. Please <a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_179983/site_179984/Documents/Signature-Field-Trips.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">see our signature field trips flyer</a> for more information.</p></div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem" id="dreambox">
	<div class="newstitle">DreamBox</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class=""><p class="">If you are looking for an additional math resource for your child all Littleton students now have access to DreamBox. DreamBox is an online math program that will supplement the instruction provided in the weekly instructional packets. To access Dreambox, have your child <a href="https://clever.com/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&amp;district_id=53602bbd8a19c9180e00432a&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fclever.com%2Fin%2Fauth_callback&amp;client_id=4c63c1cf623dce82caac&amp;state=b9cd76f25b075ea66a2f8cd23ef4f1a70f60ad5c6d853c6744ee60b6c05d0ce" title="" alt="" target="_blank">log in to Clever</a> and follow the instructions on the flyer you will find there.</p></div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem" id="enrollment">
	<div class="newstitle">Enrollment</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class=""><p class="">Are you new to the community? Need to enroll your child in school for either this year or next school year? We are still enrolling. If you need assistance, send an email to <a href="mailto:registrar@littletonaz.org" title="" alt="" target="_top">registrar@littletonaz.org</a> and one of our enrollment specialists will be able to help you.</p></div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem" id="remindinstructions">
	<div class="newstitle">Remind Instructions</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class="">
<p class="">Our teachers have been using Remind to contact families regarding the next steps for remote learning. Don’t miss important updates to help support your child’s learning during the school closure. If you haven’t signed up for Remind, attached you will find instructions on how to register. We know that remote learning puts an additional burden on our families and we want to assure you that we will continue to work as partners to keep your child academically engaged.</p>
<p class="">Nuestros maestros han estado utilizando Remind para comunicarse con las familias sobre los próximos pasos para el aprendizaje remoto. No se pierda actualizaciones importantes para ayudar a apoyar el aprendizaje de su hijo(a) durante el cierre de la escuela. Si no se ha registrado en Remind, adjunto encontrará instrucciones sobre cómo registrarse. Sabemos que el aprendizaje remoto supone una carga adicional para nuestras familias y queremos asegurarle que continuaremos trabajando como socios para mantener a su hijo involucrado académicamente. </p>
<ul>
<li class=""><a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_179983/site_179984/Documents/Remind-Flyer.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">Remind Instructions Flyer</a></li>
<li class=""><a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_179983/site_179984/Documents/Remind-Flyer-Spanish.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank" class="">Remind Instructions Flyer - Spanish</a></li>
</ul>
<p></p>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem" id="communityresources">
	<div class="newstitle">Community Resources During COVID-19 Pandemic</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class="">
<p class="">Below is a list of community resources to help you during this difficult time. Here you will find information on free meals for children, food pantry and food boxes, local take out deals, as well as emotional support resources. Please stay safe, and we will get through this together.</p>
<p class=""></p>
<ul><li class=""><a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_179983/site_179984/Documents/Community-Resources.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">Community Resources</a></li></ul>
</div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem" id="academiclearning">
	<div class="newstitle">Resources for Academic Learning</div>
	<div class="newsbody">
<p class="">Many of you have inquired about online resources to keep your child academically engaged during the school closure. Here is a list of online resources broken out by grade levels and subjects that you can use. Many of the activities listed on the Choice Board Activities sheet require no technology.</p>
<ul class="">
<li class=""><a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_179983/site_179984/Documents/Choice-Board-Activities.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">Choice Board Activities</a></li>
<li class=""><a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_179983/site_179984/Documents/Resources-for-Families-Phase-1.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">Resources for Families</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem" id="">
	<div class="newstitle">Register to Vote</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><p class="">To register to vote, please follow the directions on the <a href="https://azsos.gov/elections/voting-election/register-vote-or-update-your-current-voter-information" title="" alt="" target="_blank">registration website</a>.</p></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem" id="evasbistro">
	<div class="newstitle">Eva's Bistro</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><p class="">Eva's Bistro is open to the public and serves breakfast and lunch on school days. Check out our <a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_179983/site_179984/Documents/Bistro-Menu.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">menu</a>, and come join us for food that's good for the soul!</p></div>
</div>
</div>
